# Local-only booking page v2 preview. The route was reverted on remote
# (see commit reverting 2fae0c2) but the file is kept locally for the
# owner to iterate on before deciding to re-ship it. Brackets in the
# slug folder name are escaped so .gitignore treats them as literal
# characters, not glob character classes.
/app/book/\[slug\]/v2/
